            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">2. The depressed patient has ingestion of a big quantity of Aspirin 6 hours ago, came to the emergency room with complaints of nauesa,vomiting, increase respiration, investigation showed highly elevated level of ASA(its 200mg/dl), what is your action?</p>"
